##################### Translations #####################
## For translators:

This tutorial describes how to create translations for Moneychanger (and Qt-Applications in general):
http://qt-project.org/doc/qt-4.8/linguist-translators.html

To add a new lanuage make a copy of Translations/en_US.ts to start from.
If you have created a new file add it to moneychanger.pro in the section TRANSLATIONS or ask the maintainer.


## For release manager:

If some UI stuff has changed do:
  lupdate moneychanger.pro -ts Translations/*
Now handle the generated files to the translators.

For new releases do
  lrelease moneychanger.pro
and add all the generated .qm-Files to the "translations"-folder in the install directory.

More informations:
http://qt-project.org/doc/qt-4.8/linguist-manager.html

